we're really excited why neural networks are so great but the issue is if i take that again the

00:57:31.300 --> 00:57:35.920
same network i just trained it on dogs and previously trained it on cats i try and test it

00:57:36.260 --> 00:57:41.580
on cats again it's gonna forget pretty much everything it learned about cats and this is an

00:57:41.720 --> 00:57:46.480
old old problem back in like you know the good old days when neural networks were connectionist

00:57:46.650 --> 00:57:51.700
models and yeah yeah yeah computer scientists it was the cognitive scientists yeah it's like

00:57:51.700 --> 00:57:57.620
over over training or something like that right kind of overfitting related yeah it's very similar

